{
  "video_id": "ciDjhKKxOaY",
  "title": "How to train employees to have difficult conversations | Tamekia MizLadi Smith",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12968.0,
      "end_time": 15166.0,
      "text": "We live in a world where the collection of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15190.0,
      "end_time": 17738.0,
      "text": "is happening 24 hours a day, seven days a week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17762.0,
      "end_time": 20550.0,
      "text": "365 days a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20730.0,
      "end_time": 25530.0,
      "text": "This data is usually collected by what we call a front-desk specialist now."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25770.0,
      "end_time": 28197.0,
      "text": "These are the retail clerks at your favorite department stores,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28221.0,
      "end_time": 30664.0,
      "text": "the cashiers at the grocery stores,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30688.0,
      "end_time": 33293.0,
      "text": "the registration specialists at the hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33317.0,
      "end_time": 36431.0,
      "text": "and even the person that sold you your last movie ticket."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36908.0,
      "end_time": 40783.0,
      "text": "They ask discreet questions, like: \"May I please have your zip code?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40807.0,
      "end_time": 43918.0,
      "text": "Or, \"Would you like to use your savings card today?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44369.0,
      "end_time": 46678.0,
      "text": "All of which gives us data."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46702.0,
      "end_time": 51289.0,
      "text": "However, the conversation becomes a little bit more complex"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51313.0,
      "end_time": 54631.0,
      "text": "when the more difficult questions need to be asked."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54655.0,
      "end_time": 56448.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you a story, see."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56750.0,
      "end_time": 59768.0,
      "text": "Once upon a time, there was a woman named Miss Margaret."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59792.0,
      "end_time": 61943.0,
      "text": "Miss Margaret had been a front-desk specialist"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61967.0,
      "end_time": 63427.0,
      "text": "for almost 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63451.0,
      "end_time": 67268.0,
      "text": "And in all that time, she has never, and I do mean never,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67292.0,
      "end_time": 70812.0,
      "text": "had to ask a patient their gender, race or ethnicity."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70836.0,
      "end_time": 74590.0,
      "text": "Because, see, now Miss Margaret has the ability to just look at you."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74830.0,
      "end_time": 75241.0,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75265.0,
      "end_time": 78420.0,
      "text": "And she can tell if you are a boy or a girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78660.0,
      "end_time": 81303.0,
      "text": "black or white, American or non-American."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81327.0,
      "end_time": 84565.0,
      "text": "And in her mind, those were the only categories."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84589.0,
      "end_time": 86605.0,
      "text": "So imagine that grave day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86629.0,
      "end_time": 91522.0,
      "text": "when her sassy supervisor invited her to this \"change everything\" meeting"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91546.0,
      "end_time": 95180.0,
      "text": "and told her that would have to ask each and every last one of her patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95204.0,
      "end_time": 96609.0,
      "text": "to self-identify."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96633.0,
      "end_time": 101402.0,
      "text": "She gave her six genders, eight races and over 100 ethnicities."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101427.0,
      "end_time": 104150.0,
      "text": "Well, now, Miss Margaret was appalled."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104390.0,
      "end_time": 105436.0,
      "text": "I mean, highly offended."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105460.0,
      "end_time": 108791.0,
      "text": "So much so that she marched down to that human-resource department"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108815.0,
      "end_time": 111339.0,
      "text": "to see if she was eligible for an early retirement."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111363.0,
      "end_time": 113323.0,
      "text": "And she ended her rant by saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113347.0,
      "end_time": 118217.0,
      "text": "that her sassy supervisor invited her to this \"change everything\" meeting"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118241.0,
      "end_time": 120265.0,
      "text": "and didn't, didn't, even, even"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120289.0,
      "end_time": 123317.0,
      "text": "bring, bring food, food, food, food."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123341.0,
      "end_time": 124494.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124519.0,
      "end_time": 129586.0,
      "text": "(Applause) (Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 130681.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133115.0,
      "text": "You know you've got to bring food to these meetings."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133139.0,
      "end_time": 135482.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135506.0,
      "end_time": 136665.0,
      "text": "Anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136689.0,
      "end_time": 138197.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 138221.0,
      "end_time": 140990.0,
      "text": "Now, that was an example of a healthcare setting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141140.0,
      "end_time": 144347.0,
      "text": "but of course, all businesses collect some form of data."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144371.0,
      "end_time": 147513.0,
      "text": "True story: I was going to wire some money."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148165.0,
      "end_time": 150720.0,
      "text": "And the customer service representative asked me"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150744.0,
      "end_time": 153780.0,
      "text": "if I was born in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 153419.0,
      "end_time": 155800.0,
      "text": "Now, I hesitated to answer her question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 155824.0,
      "end_time": 158954.0,
      "text": "and before she even realized why I hesitated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 158978.0,
      "end_time": 161993.0,
      "text": "she began to throw the company she worked for under the bus."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 162170.0,
      "end_time": 167890.0,
      "text": "She said, \"Girl, I know it's stupid, but they makin' us ask this question.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167113.0,
      "end_time": 168264.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168288.0,
      "end_time": 170361.0,
      "text": "Because of the way she presented it to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170385.0,
      "end_time": 171984.0,
      "text": "I was like, \"Girl, why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172561.0,
      "end_time": 174791.0,
      "text": "Why they makin' you ask this question?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174815.0,
      "end_time": 176617.0,
      "text": "Is they deportin' people?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 176641.0,
      "end_time": 178783.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 178807.0,
      "end_time": 181290.0,
      "text": "But then I had to turn on the other side of me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 181530.0,
      "end_time": 183621.0,
      "text": "the more professional speaker-poet side of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 184164.0,
      "end_time": 188314.0,
      "text": "The one that understood that there were little Miss Margarets all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 188871.0,
      "end_time": 191839.0,
      "text": "People who were good people, maybe even good employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191863.0,
      "end_time": 194415.0,
      "text": "but lacked the ability to ask their questions properly"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 194439.0,
      "end_time": 196974.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately, that made her look bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 196998.0,
      "end_time": 200244.0,
      "text": "but the worst, that made the business look even worse"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 200268.0,
      "end_time": 201934.0,
      "text": "than how she was looking."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202236.0,
      "end_time": 204300.0,
      "text": "Because she had no idea who I was."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 204270.0,
      "end_time": 207712.0,
      "text": "I mean, I literally could have been a woman who was scheduled to do a TED Talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 207736.0,
      "end_time": 209513.0,
      "text": "and would use her as an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209538.0,
      "end_time": 210838.0,
      "text": "Imagine that."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210862.0,
      "end_time": 215124.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215148.0,
      "end_time": 216331.0,
      "text": "And unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 216355.0,
      "end_time": 219250.0,
      "text": "what happens is people would decline to answer the questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 219274.0,
      "end_time": 221783.0,
      "text": "because they feel like you would use the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221807.0,
      "end_time": 223232.0,
      "text": "to discriminate against them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 223256.0,
      "end_time": 225647.0,
      "text": "all because of how you presented the information."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 225671.0,
      "end_time": 227448.0,
      "text": "And at that point, we get bad data."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 227473.0,
      "end_time": 229584.0,
      "text": "And everybody knows what bad data does."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229608.0,
      "end_time": 232401.0,
      "text": "Bad data costs you time, it costs you money"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 232425.0,
      "end_time": 234371.0,
      "text": "and it costs you resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 234395.0,
      "end_time": 236958.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, when you have bad data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 236982.0,
      "end_time": 240610.0,
      "text": "it also costs you a lot more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 240850.0,
      "end_time": 242480.0,
      "text": "because we have health disparities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 242504.0,
      "end_time": 244718.0,
      "text": "and we have social determinants of health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 244742.0,
      "end_time": 246399.0,
      "text": "and we have the infant mortality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 246424.0,
      "end_time": 249670.0,
      "text": "all of which depends on the data that we collect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249910.0,
      "end_time": 252339.0,
      "text": "and if we have bad data, than we have those issues still."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 252363.0,
      "end_time": 254262.0,
      "text": "And we have underprivileged populations"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 254286.0,
      "end_time": 257770.0,
      "text": "that remain unfortunate and underprivileged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 257101.0,
      "end_time": 261270.0,
      "text": "because the data that we're using is either outdated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 261510.0,
      "end_time": 264344.0,
      "text": "or is not good at all or we don't have anything at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 264987.0,
      "end_time": 267623.0,
      "text": "Now, wouldn't it be amazing if people like Miss Margaret"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 267647.0,
      "end_time": 270796.0,
      "text": "and the customer-service representative at the wiring place"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 270821.0,
      "end_time": 275195.0,
      "text": "were graced to collect data with compassionate care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 275562.0,
      "end_time": 277879.0,
      "text": "Can I explain to you what I mean by \"graced?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 278324.0,
      "end_time": 279990.0,
      "text": "I wrote an acrostic poem."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 280300.0,
      "end_time": 285730.0,
      "text": "G: Getting the front desk specialist involved and letting them know"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 285970.0,
      "end_time": 289490.0,
      "text": "R: the Relevance of their role as they become"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 289740.0,
      "end_time": 292605.0,
      "text": "A: Accountable for the accuracy of data while implementing"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 292629.0,
      "end_time": 296673.0,
      "text": "C: Compassionate care within all encounters by becoming"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 296697.0,
      "end_time": 299998.0,
      "text": "E: Equipped with the education needed to inform people"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 300220.0,
      "end_time": 303315.0,
      "text": "of why data collection is so important."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 304315.0,
      "end_time": 307264.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 307288.0,
      "end_time": 309384.0,
      "text": "Now, I'm an artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 309408.0,
      "end_time": 311820.0,
      "text": "And so what happens with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 311106.0,
      "end_time": 313280.0,
      "text": "is that when I create something artistically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 313304.0,
      "end_time": 315227.0,
      "text": "the trainer in me is awakened as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 315251.0,
      "end_time": 319323.0,
      "text": "So what I did was, I began to develop that acrostic poem into a full training"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 319347.0,
      "end_time": 320895.0,
      "text": "entitled \"I'm G.R.A.C.E.D.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 320919.0,
      "end_time": 323760.0,
      "text": "Because I remember, being the front-desk specialist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 323784.0,
      "end_time": 326457.0,
      "text": "and when I went to the office of equity to start working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 326482.0,
      "end_time": 330370.0,
      "text": "I was like, \"Is that why they asked us to ask that question?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 330610.0,
      "end_time": 331828.0,
      "text": "It all became a bright light to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 331853.0,
      "end_time": 335490.0,
      "text": "and I realized that I asked people and I told people about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 335514.0,
      "end_time": 338798.0,
      "text": "I called them by the wrong gender, I called them by the wrong race,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 338822.0,
      "end_time": 340625.0,
      "text": "I called them by the wrong ethnicity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 340649.0,
      "end_time": 342656.0,
      "text": "and the environment became hostile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 342680.0,
      "end_time": 346964.0,
      "text": "people was offended and I was frustrated because I was not graced."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 346988.0,
      "end_time": 349575.0,
      "text": "I remember my computerized training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 349599.0,
      "end_time": 355224.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately, that training did not prepare me to deescalate a situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 355249.0,
      "end_time": 358625.0,
      "text": "It did not prepare me to have teachable moments when I had questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 358649.0,
      "end_time": 360307.0,
      "text": "about asking the questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 360331.0,
      "end_time": 363895.0,
      "text": "I would look at the computer and say, \"So, what do I do when this happens?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 363919.0,
      "end_time": 365777.0,
      "text": "And the computer would say ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 365801.0,
      "end_time": 369680.0,
      "text": "nothing, because a computer cannot talk back to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 369930.0,
      "end_time": 372300.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 372324.0,
      "end_time": 374895.0,
      "text": "So that's the importance of having someone there"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 374919.0,
      "end_time": 377695.0,
      "text": "who was trained to teach you and tell you what you do"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 377720.0,
      "end_time": 379410.0,
      "text": "in situations like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 380300.0,
      "end_time": 382655.0,
      "text": "So, when I created the \"I'm G.R.A.C.E.D\" training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 382680.0,
      "end_time": 385674.0,
      "text": "I created it with that experience that I had in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 385698.0,
      "end_time": 388214.0,
      "text": "but also that conviction that I had in mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 388238.0,
      "end_time": 390491.0,
      "text": "Because I wanted the instructional design of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 390515.0,
      "end_time": 393293.0,
      "text": "to be a safe space for open dialogue for people."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 393317.0,
      "end_time": 395212.0,
      "text": "I wanted to talk about biases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 395236.0,
      "end_time": 397633.0,
      "text": "the unconscious ones and the conscious ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 397657.0,
      "end_time": 398823.0,
      "text": "and what we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 398847.0,
      "end_time": 402791.0,
      "text": "Because now I know that when you engage people in the why,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 402815.0,
      "end_time": 406291.0,
      "text": "it challenges their perspective, and it changes their attitudes."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 406315.0,
      "end_time": 409474.0,
      "text": "Now I know that data that we have at the front desk"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 409498.0,
      "end_time": 414311.0,
      "text": "translates into research that eliminates disparities and finds cures."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 414335.0,
      "end_time": 418410.0,
      "text": "Now I know that teaching people transitional change"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 418650.0,
      "end_time": 420911.0,
      "text": "instead of shocking them into change"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 420935.0,
      "end_time": 424190.0,
      "text": "is always a better way of implementing change."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 424214.0,
      "end_time": 427260.0,
      "text": "See, now I know people are more likely to share information"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 427284.0,
      "end_time": 431143.0,
      "text": "when they are treated with respect by knowledgeable staff members."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 431167.0,
      "end_time": 434188.0,
      "text": "Now I know that you don't have to be a statistician"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 434212.0,
      "end_time": 437212.0,
      "text": "to understand the power and the purpose of data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 437237.0,
      "end_time": 441601.0,
      "text": "but you do have to treat people with respect and have compassionate care."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 441625.0,
      "end_time": 444450.0,
      "text": "Now I know that when you've been graced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 444474.0,
      "end_time": 447849.0,
      "text": "it is your responsibility to empower somebody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 447874.0,
      "end_time": 450299.0,
      "text": "But most importantly, now I know"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 450323.0,
      "end_time": 452736.0,
      "text": "that when teaching human beings"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 452760.0,
      "end_time": 455839.0,
      "text": "to communicate with other human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 455863.0,
      "end_time": 459648.0,
      "text": "it should be delivered by a human being."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 460117.0,
      "end_time": 466909.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 466933.0,
      "end_time": 468782.0,
      "text": "So when y'all go to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 468806.0,
      "end_time": 472140.0,
      "text": "and y'all schedule that \"change everything\" meeting --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 472165.0,
      "end_time": 473815.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 473839.0,
      "end_time": 475354.0,
      "text": "remember Miss Margaret."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 475792.0,
      "end_time": 479611.0,
      "text": "And don't forget the food, the food, the food, the food."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 480103.0,
      "end_time": 481254.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 481278.0,
      "end_time": 486753.0,
      "text": "(Applause) (Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 486777.0,
      "end_time": 487952.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 487976.0,
      "end_time": 489571.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}